rows.label: bf08100100_0030
rows.name:
I'm Kagutsuchi. But I hardly needed to introduce
myself to you, did I?

rows.label: bf08100100_0040
rows.name:
You must know practically all there is to know
about me by now.

rows.label: bf08100100_0050
rows.name: I just wanted to make sure if the me that you knew,

rows.label: bf08100100_0060
rows.name: and the me written here are the same.

rows.label: bf08100100_0080
rows.name: People glorify themselves in their own diaries right?
